As for the graduated license, the G2 in Ontario is basically the full license 'cept no alcohol and no more passengers than seatbelts. In fact, I put off getting the full G license so long that my road test was the day that my G2 expired.... You should have to take a road test every 10 years to stay licensed. /sigh.<br>
